King Movement
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a Maori attempt from the late 1850s to achieve unity of purpose and action under the guidance of a single leader, the Maori King
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
